project.name: Model List Difference
project.description: Creates a model list that is the difference of two or more other model lists.

gallery-model-list-difference.name: gallery-model-list-difference
gallery-model-list-difference.description: Creates a model list that is the difference of two or more other model lists.

classitems.description:
Creates a model list that is the difference of two or more other model
lists.  The new model list stays up to date as the source lists change.
classitems.name: difference

params.name: modelListType
params.description:
Optional.  The first
argument determines the type of model list that is created; it may be a
constructor function or a string namespace to a constructor function
stored on Y. If the first argument is an instance of ModelList, its
constructor is used.

params.name: modelLists
params.description:
1-n ModelList objects to difference.  Order is
important.
